Name: Snatch
Effect: Single Target. Reaction 6. Remove any Increase/Reduction on the Foe's Attributes, Active Shield Moves, Healing effects on the Foe, or effects on its side of the field; and place them on te User instead. See p. 531 for more info.
Description: The User takes notice of the good stuff on the other side and quickly takes them for itself. Finders keepers, losers weepers!
